entries.title: Sam Bankman-Fried will now surrender himself for extradition before Bahamian court Monday: Source
entries.description: Founder and former FTX CEO Sam Bankman-Fried will not contest extradition to the U.S. in an about face just days after being remanded to Bahamas prison.
